                                <button class="button button-primary">Borrow</button>
                            </footer>
                        </article>
                    </li>

                    <li class="card">
                        <img src="Images/sidereal.webp" class="images" alt="Catan board game package">
                        <article class="content">
                            <h1>Sidereal Confluence</h1>
                            <p>This is a short description of the game.</p>
                            <footer class="button-container">
                                <button class="button button-primary">Borrow</button>
                            </footer>
                        </article>
                    </li>

                    <li class="card">
                        <img src="Images/starRealms.webp" class="images" alt="Catan board game package">
                        <article class="content">
                            <h1>Star Realms</h1>
                            <p>This is a short description of the game.</p>
